Apple’s iPhone 17 Pro models are selling very well, possibly better than any model before. And there are good reasons why. Its cameras are fantastic, the battery life is better than ever, and they have double the storage space compared to last year.

But in the midst of all this excitement, I can’t help but point out a few things about Apple's iPhone 17 Pro that bothers me, and I don’t think are getting enough attention.
title: iPhone 17 Pro: Less Features For More Money
